The author also briefly touches upon the human-computer interaction aspect of software engineering, which could be relevant to the sub-category of cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the author mentions the potential problems and challenges in large software projects, which could be relevant to the sub-category of cs.CY (Computers and Society).
